 &lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table></description></item><item><title>firestore-query-collection</title><link>https://xxsc0529.github.io/genai-toolbox/resources/tools/firestore/firestore-query-collection/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://xxsc0529.github.io/genai-toolbox/resources/tools/firestore/firestore-query-collection/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="about">About&lt;/h1>
